                <h2>About</h2>
                <p>The aging of our beloved ones faces us to the laws of life: taking affectively of them. But this
                    reality faces us that most of the time we spend it in routine and repetitive work and the quality
                    time that we want to give them was replaced with cumbersome procedures, reminders, visits
                </p>
                <p>With this in our minds, we figured out a need to develop a device that can take care of this tasks
                    which were a big load for people who takes care of elder persons, in special women.
                </p>
                <p>That’s how <strong>arquitas</strong> was created.</p>
            </div>
