            <div class="about-2-texto ">
             
                <p>This device will stop the necessity of human care once and for all. Would make more much easier the
                    relation between families, elder people and caregivers. Besides, the community that forms among
                    users of Arquitas greatly stimulates the reason for living of these people. At the same time, it
                    will save both families and medical institutions a lot of resources. And you'll reduce your
                    environmental impact and carbon footprint by drastically reducing travel.
                </p>
                <p>That’s why we are convinced that a better life is possible.</p>
